All based on classes of Fastcampus

main_grid1.html & main_grid1.css
are for learning about 'grid container properties' especially about position of each grid

main_grid2.html & main_grid2.css
are for learning about 'grid-template-areas'

main_grid3.html & main_grid3.css
are for learning about 'grid items' especially about row & column size with content of item. we can set the max size of 'fit-content'.
also there's a 'min-content' & 'max-content' which can make size as small/big as item can be, instead of using 'fit-content(max-size)'.
if you want to change the line depending on space between letters then use this function mentioned below.
'word-break: keep-all'
